com.hyperwallet.android.listener

Interface HyperwalletListener<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the domain object type expected as a response to a successful request

    public interface HyperwalletListener<T>
    The listener interface for receiving completion events from the Hyperwallet Core SDK.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods
